        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl2_Label1"><p>Google Cloud Storage is the Google online storage service that allows you to store files and backups on the Google Cloud Platform infrastructure. Like all the most well-known Cloud services based on a pay-per-use model, therefore on the actual use of storage and bandwidth, Google Cloud Storage allows the remote saving of large amounts of data [&hellip;]</p>
</span><a id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl2_HyperLink2" href="https://www.iperiusbackup.net/en/how-to-make-a-backup-to-google-cloud-storage/" target="_blank">Read more »»</a> 
