            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl4_Label1"><p>BitLocker allows you to encrypt any hard disk connected to a PC or Windows Server, including removable drives such as USB or RDX. The protection mode is widely described in the article BitLocker: drive encryption on Windows 10 with a recovery key In this tutorial, we will see how to restore an image of a drive [&hellip;]</p>
</span><a id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl4_HyperLink2" href="https://www.iperiusbackup.net/en/restore-a-bitlocker-drive-image-backup-with-iperius-recovery-enviroment/" target="_blank">Read more »»</a> 
